# Dmitriyevka, Beloozersky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Dmitriyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Beloozersky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 127 as of 2010.
Geography
It is located 21&nbsp;km from Krasnousolsky and 5&nbsp;km from Beloye Ozero.
